\begin_inset Formula $\betaa\nu(y)$
\end_inset

 in 
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:12"

\end_inset

.
 Therefore the region of 
\begin_inset Formula $Y$
\end_inset

 with negative 
\begin_inset Formula $\d\J/\d\Lambda$
\end_inset

 is smaller.
 
\end_layout

